{{wikipediapar|Coming out}}
{{wikipediapar|The closet}}

===Intransitive verb phrase===
'''to [[come]] [[out]] [[of]] the [[closet]]'''

#{{idiom}} To tell others about one's [[homosexuality]] or [[bisexuality]] where previously this had been kept [[secret]].
#(''by extension'') To tell others about any minority or disapproved-of belief, preference, etc., where previously this had been kept secret.
#:''She finally '''came out of the closet''' to her religious family regarding her atheism.''

